emove":0,"can_add":0,"can_edit":0,"can_publish":0,"can_get_doi":0,"can_share":1,"can_move":1,"can_move_outside":1,"can_transfer":1,"can_download":1,"is_locked":0},"guid":"C4EC27B989B74728BFAF0ED628280E36","state_version_id":182,"steps":[{"id":1090084,"guid":"5A41E8AAD8A14649B245FF8F7E4C90AF","previous_id":null,"previous_guid":null,"modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"1717052EE257472395F0D8403C4A5849","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":"Design sgRNA and order PCR oligos."}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"4D0575EB026B4E229475BE1A295DC176","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">Add\u00a0the desired protospacer sequence to the T7FwdVar oligo and order the oligo from your favorite oligonucleotide supplier. There are many programs available for protospacer design that attempt to optimize on- and\/or off-target activity. Which program is most useful depends upon many factors including type of editing, organism being edited, etc. Choice of protospacer design program is beyond the scope of this protocol.<\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-style:italic;\">The transcript will start with the bolded G just 5\u2019 of the dashes in the T7FwdVar oligo. T7 RNA polymerase requires a 5\u2019 G for proper transcript initiation. If your protospacer has a G at the 5\u2019 end, you can omit it from the T7FwdVar design to avoid duplication of the G. If your protospacer has a C, T, or A at the 5\u2019 end, add the whole protospacer sequence to T7FwdVar. In this case, there will be an extra G added to the 5\u2019 end of the protospacer, but literature indicates this will have minimal effect unless your guide is very short.<\/span><span><\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Primers:\u00a0<\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span>T7FwdVar oligo (5\u2019-TAATACGACTCACTATA<\/span><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">G<\/span><span>--protospacer sequence\u2014GTTTCAGAGCTATGCTGGAAAC-3\u2019 )<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\">T7RevLong oligo (5\u2019-AAAAAAAGCACCGACTCGGTGCCACTTTTTCAAGTTGATAACGGACTAGCCTTATTTCAACTTGCTATGCTGTTTCCAGCATAGCTCTGA-3\u2019 )<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">T7FwdAmp primer (5\u2019-TAATACGACTCACTATAG-3\u2019)<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">T7RevAmp primer (5\u2019-AAAAAAAGCACCGACTCGGTGC-3\u2019 )<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"html":null,"section":null,"section_color":null,"section_duration":0,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":1090085,"guid":"BB71D41E792B4FCD958CCDF2DA0AA790","previous_id":1090084,"previous_guid":"5A41E8AAD8A14649B245FF8F7E4C90AF","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"8064F317124548298710A35A0228C4B5","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":"Generate in vitro transcription DNA template"}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"AE317CD9BB514D06B70B250EC43FBF16","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">For each\u00a0T7FwdVar oligo you designed, set up the following PCR (total volume should be 20.0 \u00b5L). Make sure everything is RNase free and filter tips are used. Furthermore, wipe down everything (in every step of protocol) with RNase Away to ensure no contamination with RNAse.\u00a0<\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span>10.6 \u00b5l DEPC-treated H<\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:sub;\">2<\/span><span>O<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"> 4.0 uL 5x Phusion HF Buffer \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/div><div class = \"text-block\"> 0.4 \u00b5l 10 mM dNTPs\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/div><div class = \"text-block\"> 0.4 \u00b5l T7FwdVar (1 \u00b5M)\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/div><div class = \"text-block\"> 0.4 \u00b5l T7RevLong (1 \u00b5M)\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/div><div class = \"text-block\"> 2 \u00b5l T7FwdAmp (10 \u00b5M)\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0 <\/div><div class = \"text-block\"> 2 \u00b5l T7RevAmp (10 \u00b5M)\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0 <\/div><div class = \"text-block\"> 0.2 \u00b5l Phusion HF DNA polymerase (2u\/\u00b5l)<\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-style:italic;\">If making multiple sgRNA templates, prepare a master mix with all components except T7FwdVar. Include a no template control (omit T7FwdVar).<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Primers:\u00a0<\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span>T7FwdVar oligo (5\u2019-TAATACGACTCACTATA<\/span><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">G<\/span><span>--protospacer sequence\u2014GTTTCAGAGCTATGCTGGAAAC-3\u2019 )<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\">T7RevLong oligo (5\u2019-AAAAAAAGCACCGACTCGGTGCCACTTTTTCAAGTTGATAACGGACTAGCCTTATTTCAACTTGCTATGCTGTTTCCAGCATAGCTCTGA-3\u2019 )<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">T7FwdAmp primer (5\u2019-TAATACGACTCACTATAG-3\u2019)<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">T7RevAmp primer (5\u2019-AAAAAAAGCACCGACTCGGTGC-3\u2019 )<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"html":null,"section":null,"section_color":null,"section_duration":0,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":1090086,"guid":"29BA10613E0F4FB3B0C171F1D1F36870","previous_id":1090085,"previous_guid":"BB71D41E792B4FCD958CCDF2DA0AA790","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"7774BD5B4E794D29B5EEF62DB93D8DD7","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":"In vitro transcription DNA template PCR"}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"9724F77F135F42F4A7607F1D945393AD","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">Run PCR:<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">98\u02da 30 sec<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">98\u02da 10 sec <\/div><div class = \"text-block\">51\u02da 10 sec \u00a0<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">72\u02da 10 sec<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a030x steps 2-4<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">72\u02da 2 min<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">4\u02da hold<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">No PCR cleanup necessary at this point<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"html":null,"section":null,"section_color":null,"section_duration":0,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":1090087,"guid":"CF54E9D7C3E84E26BDF6D8EF89F89F9B","previous_id":1090086,"previous_guid":"29BA10613E0F4FB3B0C171F1D1F36870","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"E8797727308E4BAB8582BDE5818996BE","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":"In vitro T7 transcription"}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"F76F56457C8B47A9BA799902B212F8F5","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">We like to use HiScribe T7 High Yield RNA Synthesis Kit but any T7 RNA synthesis kit should be fine.<\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span>Mix the following to make <\/span><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">20 \u00b5l<\/span><span> total\u00a0T7 transcription\u00a0mix<\/span><\/div><table border><tr style = \"text-align:center;\"><td>  <\/td><td>A<\/td><td>B<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">1<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">volume<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">reagent<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">2<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">2 \u00b5l<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">10x Buffer 1x<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">3<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">2 \u00b5l<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">ATP (100 mM), 10 mM<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">4<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">2 \u00b5l<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">GTP (100 mM), 10 mM<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">5<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">2 \u00b5l<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">CTP (100 mM), 10 mM<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">6<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">2 \u00b5l<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">UTP (100 mM), 10 mM<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">7<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">8 \u00b5l<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">DNA template from Step 3, (usually ~4\u00b5g, 50 pmol)\n<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">8<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">2 \u00b5l<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">T7 RNA polymerase mix<\/td><\/tr><\/table><\/div>"}},{"id":1054725,"guid":"B7202FDF35E34749831A93BB55650C7C","order_id":2,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<table border><tr style = \"text-align:center;\"><td>  <\/td><td>A<\/td><td>B<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">1<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">volume<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">reagent<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">2<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">2 \u00b5l<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"dis